   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Greetings, my lord, that you receive a letter from me through Harpokration, that excellent fellow, so that you may at the same time know that I am grateful to him for acting for you with utmost zeal in your absence in whatever I may ask of him. He did nothing alien to his feelings for you. The vineyards, as I wrote to you also at another time, my lord, receive both cultivation and irrigation, as much as is possible. I pray for your good health.";(Verso): "To Claudius Agenor from Xenophon."</ab>
         </div>
